OL,10,     Gyear-old Jake.
OL,11,G2100FJane McDonald: From Pole to Pole
OL,12,     GOn the first South American leg,
OL,13,     GJane tours Uruguay and Brazil,
OL,14,     Genjoying a barbecue, visiting a
OL,15,     Gvineyard, taking a speedboat
OL,16,     Gtour, exploring caves and seeing
OL,17,     Gdolphins.
