OL,4,G2200FInside The Tower of London
OL,5,     GThe Tower prepares an ambitious
OL,6,     Gdisplay to celebrate the 80th
OL,7,     Ganniversary of VE day, with
OL,8,     Galmost 30,000 ceramic poppies
OL,9,     Gcascading from the top of the
OL,10,     GWhite Tower. It's no small feat!
OL,11,G2300FSusan Calman's Grand Day Out
